title: Lost My Way by Bonny Doon
lyrics:
[Verse One]
Where, where do I belong
What, what should I believe
Who oh who've I become
Do I, do I, do I even recognize me

[Chorus]
And I think somewhere along the line
I lost my way

[Verse Two]
I saw your dreaming eyes one morning when the sun came up just right
And I just want to feel all right
Doesn't matter how you get there
Doesn't matter how you get there

[Chorus]
I think somewhere along the line
I lost my way
I think somewhere along the line
I lost my way
